snippet.textDisplay: I can't even explain how great this video's timing is , I have been a dancer for almost my whole life , and just this week I had to stop dancing because I have a foot injury and also not enough time due to work and studies ... it was the most painful decision I had to make throughout my entire life , this is why I can relate to this so deeply , all the emotions in this song and video is on point to what I am feeling , it truly feels like a part of me died , I could have never explained this better , all I can say is Thank You BTS for helping me to express these feelings and for helping me heal 💜 This DESERVES more love , this is what art is all about , no one can do it better than BTS !
